'''Mk 6頭盔'''（{{lang-en|'''Mk 6 helmet'''}}）是[[英軍|英軍]]的一款制式[[戰鬥頭盔|戰鬥頭盔]]，和其自1986年起取代的舊款軍用盔——{{Link-en|Mk 3頭盔|Mk III helmet}}相比，更便於個人[[無線電|無線電]]及[[防毒面具|防毒面具]]的攜帶、對耳部保護效果亦更佳。此款頭盔由NP宇航公司（{{lang|en|NP Aerospace}}）生產<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.np-aerospace.com/ |title=website |accessdate=2013-06-05 |archive-date=2011-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110128183341/http://www.np-aerospace.com/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

Mk 6頭盔的原始用色為墨綠色，英軍另在外盔加上{{Link-en|盔套|Helmet cover}}以進行[[軍事偽裝|軍事偽裝]]，用色包含了綠色系的{{Link-en|DPM迷彩|Disruptive Pattern Material}}、叢林、沙漠圖案、用於[[極地|極地]]作戰的純白盔套及[[聯合國|聯合國]]任務的藍色盔套。有時暱稱為[[圓頂硬禮帽|戰鬥圓禮帽]]，而這詞在過去用以形容[[二戰|二戰]]時英軍的[[布洛迪鋼盔|布洛迪鋼盔]]。

Mk 6頭盔通常被誤認為是[[功夫龍|功夫龍]]製成，實際上用料是[[尼龍纖維|尼龍纖維]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?Location=U2&doc=GetTRDoc.pdf&AD=ADA215100 |title=Ballistic properties of composite materials for personnel protection MRL Technical Report MRL-TR-89-6 by J.R.Brown and G.T.Egglestone 1989 |accessdate=2013-06-05 |archive-date=2012-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121002191618/http://www.dtic.mil/cgi-bin/GetTRDoc?Location=U2&doc=GetTRDoc.pdf&AD=ADA215100 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==Mk 6A頭盔==
2005年起，Mk 6頭盔逐漸開始被原設計的更新版本——Mk 6A頭盔取代<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gnn.gov.uk/Content/Detail.asp?ReleaseID=167230&NewsAreaID=2&print=true |title=GNN - Government News Network<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-06-05 |archive-date=2008-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080228005623/http://www.gnn.gov.uk/Content/Detail.asp?ReleaseID=167230&NewsAreaID=2&print=true |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200607/cmhansrd/cm070122/text/70122w0024.htm |title=House of Commons Hansard Written Answers for 22 Jan 2007 (pt 0024) |accessdate=2013-06-05 |archive-date=2020-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627021928/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200607/cmhansrd/cm070122/text/70122w0024.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，亦由NP宇航公司生產<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.np-aerospace.com/composite-helmets/combat-helmets.htm |title=NP Aerospace Composite Helmets: Combat Helmets<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2013-06-05 |archive-date=2007-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070824053429/http://www.np-aerospace.com/composite-helmets/combat-helmets.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。儘管與Mk 6外觀十分相似，Mk 6A的彈道防護能力更好，重量也略重<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rusi.org/downloads/assets/Bain,_The_Infantry_Section.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-06-05 |archive-date=2007-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012023327/http://www.rusi.org/downloads/assets/Bain%2C_The_Infantry_Section.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

